      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="39288148">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/101822693/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u101822693-3.jpg" alt="二月二日晴" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39288148/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39288148/" class="">第61页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/101822693/" class=" " title="二月二日晴">二月二日晴</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39288148">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">明人笔记《古今事物考》称：“国朝正旦节放假五日，冬至三日，元宵十日。”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-09-24 15:13</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                明人笔记《古今事物考》称：“国朝正旦节放假五日，冬至三日，元宵十日。”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







